cu.explanation_en: Changed AMF IP address to one in the same subnet as the CU's NG interface, causing IP conflicts and routing issues.
cu.explanation_zh: 更改 AMF IP 地址為與 CU NG 接口相同子網的地址，導致 IP 衝突和路由問題。

du.explanation_en: Altered T1a_cp_dl timing parameter, leading to inconsistent timing alignment in the front-haul interface.
du.explanation_zh: 更改 T1a_cp_dl 定時參數，導致前傳接口中的定時對齊不一致。
